{
  "stem": "21089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later when the Jews were kicked out from Germany, and they took all the Jews who were not born in Germany-- this was the first act.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put on a train and unloaded on-- in a field on the Polish border, Zbaszyn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that time, groups were organized to send food to help them because they-- the Poles didn't let them in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Germans threw them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we-- I was in charge of the youth group who was in the city who was supposed to do their part.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember I was asked to supervise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a few big cases of salami, one-- sausage because can stay, doesn't get spoiled.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I supposed to go to the butcher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and those few people have been working on those things, packing it in special cases and send it to Zbaszyn for the people too.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Bread and other food article were sent because people on the field in the rain and mud and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was-- little by little, they been-- they came into the country because people have been taking them to their houses and they're allowed after a while.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I know that in our house, two families were for a short time living.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one man was, for a long time, coming always for dinners because he was living some other place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And people helped at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was organized help, all of those people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Those are the first people who have been--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the plant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He has a plant, and I was in the same profession, so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only different is that I was a little bit advanced in the profession because he had a printing plant, and I study reproduction, lithography, and other part of the industry.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
